    "description": "Are you a skilled E-commerce Executive looking for your next big career move? Cleartrip Ventures Solutions in Aurangabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Cleartrip Ventures Solutions:\nCleartrip Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cleartrip Ventures Solutions!",
